<img src="http://images.mattbutterfield.com/20110324_001.jpg" alt=" " width="850px" height="567px"/>
<p class="posttext">Crossing Lake Erie into Canada, the trip begins.</p>


<img src="http://images.mattbutterfield.com/20110324_002.jpg" alt=" " width="850px" height="567px"/>
<p class="posttext">Navigatin'</p>


<img src="http://images.mattbutterfield.com/20110324_003.jpg" alt=" " width="850px" height="567px"/>
<p class="posttext">Going wayyyy up there.</p>


<img src="http://images.mattbutterfield.com/20110324_004.jpg" alt=" " width="850px" height="567px"/>
<p class="posttext">Time to fly :)</p>


<img src="http://images.mattbutterfield.com/20110324_005.jpg" alt=" " width="850px" height="567px"/>
<p class="posttext">Made it to Goose Bay, Canada, 1000nm and six hours later.</p>


<img src="http://images.mattbutterfield.com/20110324_006.jpg" alt=" " width="850px" height="567px"/>
<p class="posttext">Freezing cold sunrise in Goose Bay. 3 degrees Fahrenheit and this was nice spring weather for them.</p>


<img src="http://images.mattbutterfield.com/20110324_007.jpg" alt=" " width="850px" height="567px"/>
<p class="posttext">Warming up the engines and almost ready to go.</p>


<img src="http://images.mattbutterfield.com/20110324_008.jpg" alt=" " width="850px" height="567px"/>
<p class="posttext">Into the blue.</p>


<img src="http://images.mattbutterfield.com/20110324_009.jpg" alt=" " width="850px" height="567px"/>
<p class="posttext">Here we go.</p>


<img src="http://images.mattbutterfield.com/20110324_010.jpg" alt=" " width="850px" height="567px"/>
<p class="posttext">A few hours later, land ho!</p>


<img src="http://images.mattbutterfield.com/20110324_011.jpg" alt=" " width="850px" height="567px"/>
<p class="posttext">Greenland!</p>


<img src="http://images.mattbutterfield.com/20110324_012.jpg" alt=" " width="850px" height="567px"/>
<p class="posttext">Greenland looks like Middle Earth.  Unbelievable.</p>


<img src="http://images.mattbutterfield.com/20110324_013.jpg" alt=" " width="850px" height="567px"/>
<p class="posttext">Our runway.  One way in, one way out.</p>


<img src="http://images.mattbutterfield.com/20110324_014.jpg" alt=" " width="850px" height="567px"/>
<p class="posttext">Final approach.</p>


<img src="http://images.mattbutterfield.com/20110324_015.jpg" alt=" " width="850px" height="567px"/>
<p class="posttext">Welcome to Narsarsuaq, Greenland.</p>


<img src="http://images.mattbutterfield.com/20110324_016.jpg" alt=" " width="850px" height="567px"/>
<p class="posttext">Our mighty steed!</p>


<img src="http://images.mattbutterfield.com/20110324_017.jpg" alt=" " width="850px" height="567px"/>
<p class="posttext">Goodbye Narsarsuaq.  On to Iceland!</p>


<img src="http://images.mattbutterfield.com/20110324_018.jpg" alt=" " width="850px" height="567px"/>
<p class="posttext">Out of the mountains.</p>


<img src="http://images.mattbutterfield.com/20110324_019.jpg" alt=" " width="850px" height="567px"/>
<p class="posttext">Greenland: Ice, snow, Glaciers.  No green whatsoever.</p>


<img src="http://images.mattbutterfield.com/20110324_020.jpg" alt=" " width="850px" height="567px"/>
<p class="posttext">My perspective for this leg.  Starting to get cold.</p>


<img src="http://images.mattbutterfield.com/20110324_021.jpg" alt=" " width="850px" height="567px"/>
<p class="posttext">Topping some weather at 20,000 ft.  Outside temp, almost -40C</p>


<img src="http://images.mattbutterfield.com/20110324_022.jpg" alt=" " width="850px" height="567px"/>
<p class="posttext">Time to descend whether we like it or not.</p>


<img src="http://images.mattbutterfield.com/20110324_023.jpg" alt=" " width="850px" height="567px"/>
<p class="posttext">Welcome to Iceland.  Living up to its name.</p>


<img src="http://images.mattbutterfield.com/20110324_024.jpg" alt=" " width="850px" height="567px"/>
<p class="posttext">Again, our mighty steed did not let us down.</p>


<img src="http://images.mattbutterfield.com/20110324_0251.jpg" alt=" " width="850px" height="567px"/>
<p class="posttext">Rest day.  Time for some exploring!</p>


<img src="http://images.mattbutterfield.com/20110324_026.jpg" alt=" " width="850px" height="567px"/>
<p class="posttext">Oh?</p>


<img src="http://images.mattbutterfield.com/20110324_027.jpg" alt=" " width="850px" height="567px"/>
<p class="posttext">Hmm...</p>


<img src="http://images.mattbutterfield.com/20110324_028.jpg" alt=" " width="850px" height="567px"/>
<p class="posttext">I see...</p>


<img src="http://images.mattbutterfield.com/20110324_029.jpg" alt=" " width="850px" height="567px"/>
<p class="posttext">Water temperature: 98-102 Fahrenheit.  Weather conditions: light snow.</p>


<img src="http://images.mattbutterfield.com/20110324_030.jpg" alt=" " width="850px" height="567px"/>
<p class="posttext">I think it is time for a swim.</p>


<img src="http://images.mattbutterfield.com/20110324_031.jpg" alt=" " width="850px" height="567px"/>
<p class="posttext">Have I mentioned that Iceland is kind of awesome?</p>


<img src="http://images.mattbutterfield.com/20110324_032.jpg" alt=" " width="567px" height="850px"/>
<p class="posttext">Iceland: give it a try sometime.  Maybe I will come back some day.</p>


<img src="http://images.mattbutterfield.com/20110324_033.jpg" alt=" " width="850px" height="567px"/>
<p class="posttext">Viewing platform.</p>


<img src="http://images.mattbutterfield.com/20110324_034.jpg" alt=" " width="850px" height="567px"/>
<p class="posttext">Goodbye Iceland!</p>


<img src="http://images.mattbutterfield.com/20110324_035.jpg" alt=" " width="850px" height="567px"/>
<p class="posttext">Time for the longest leg over water.  Very cold water.</p>


<img src="http://images.mattbutterfield.com/20110324_036.jpg" alt=" " width="850px" height="567px"/>
<p class="posttext">Weather coming in to Norway.  Awful.</p>


<img src="http://images.mattbutterfield.com/20110324_037.jpg" alt=" " width="850px" height="567px"/>
<p class="posttext">Weather coming in to Poland, clear-ish but windy.</p>


<img src="http://images.mattbutterfield.com/20110324_038.jpg" alt=" " width="850px" height="567px"/>
<p class="posttext">You have reached your destination.  The end.</p>

